  - Set INCLUDEWARNING = on

- Generated Table of Contents (TOC) settings
  - The first header level to appear in the TOC:
    - Set TOC\_MIN\_DEPTH =
      - If not set: `1`
      - Possible values: `1` to `6`
  - The last header level to appear in the TOC:
    - Set TOC\_MAX\_DEPTH =
      - If not set: `6`
      - Possible values: `1` to `6`
